 \"to\": 2061}, {\"ngram\": \"our competition venues\", \"from\": 2063, \"to\": 2085}, {\"ngram\": \"the history\", \"from\": 2102, \"to\": 2113}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2117, \"to\": 2126}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We wanted excitement, we got passion.\", \"from\": 2128, \"to\": 2165, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"excitement\", \"from\": 2138, \"to\": 2148}, {\"ngram\": \"passion\", \"from\": 2157, \"to\": 2164}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We wanted to be inspired, we got L\\u00e9on Marchand.\", \"from\": 2167, \"to\": 2215, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2201, \"end\": 2214, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/L\\u00e9on_Marchand\", \"score\": 0.9999997803538704, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"L\\u00e9on Marchand\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/L\\u00e9on_Marchand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/L\\u00e9on_Marchand\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Together, we have experienced Games like nothing the world has seen before.\\\"\", \"from\": 2216, \"to\": 2292, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Games\", \"from\": 2246, \"to\": 2251}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 2257, \"to\": 2264}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2265, \"to\": 2274}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Estanguet, who won three Olympic golds in the canoe slalom between 2000 and 2012, said: \\\"It would be a little bit like a spoiled brat saying 'I have got regrets about the Olympic Games', it's not the case.\", \"from\": 2294, \"to\": 2499, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Estanguet\", \"from\": 2294, \"to\": 2303}, {\"ngram\": \"three Olympic golds\", \"from\": 2313, \"to\": 2332}, {\"ngram\": \"the canoe slalom\", \"from\": 2336, \"to\": 2352}, {\"ngram\": \"a spoiled brat\", \"from\": 2413, \"to\": 2427}, {\"ngram\": \"regrets\", \"from\": 2447, \"to\": 2454}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2461, \"to\": 2478}, {\"ngram\": \"the case\", \"from\": 2490, \"to\": 2498}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Yes, I was an athlete and I am a perfectionist, I can be a little bit of a nitpicker.\", \"from\": 2501, \"to\": 2587, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 2513, \"to\": 2523}, {\"ngram\": \"a perfectionist\", \"from\": 2533, \"to\": 2548}, {\"ngram\": \"a little bit\", \"from\": 2559, \"to\": 2571}, {\"ngram\": \"a nitpicker\", \"from\": 2575, \"to\": 2586}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I know things were not perfect.\", \"from\": 2588, \"to\": 2619, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 2595, \"to\": 2601}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We had issues, things that needed to be fine-tuned.\", \"from\": 2620, \"to\": 2671, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"issues\", \"from\": 2627, \"to\": 2633}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 2635, \"to\": 2641}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There are always things that could be improved and we have had issues day-in day-out to resolve.\", \"from\": 2673, \"to\": 2770, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 2691, \"to\": 2697}, {\"ngram\": \"issues\", \"from\": 2737, \"to\": 2743}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But if someone told me on the eve of the opening ceremony of how things would go, I would have said 'sign me up'.\", \"from\": 2772, \"to\": 2886, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 2780, \"to\": 2787}, {\"ngram\": \"the eve\", \"from\": 2799, \"to\": 2806}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 2810, \"to\": 2830}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 2838, \"to\": 2844}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's wonderful, it's a huge success, a collective success, incredibly so.\", \"from\": 2887, \"to\": 2960, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a huge success\", \"from\": 2908, \"to\": 2922}, {\"ngram\": \"a collective success\", \"from\": 2924, \"to\": 2944}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"France has rallied together to pull off this edition of the Ol